  "id": "RAW_977f5f5d",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-12-9）：清华大学与中科院开源 LLaVA-UHD，PVC 渐进视觉压缩技术实现多模态模型高效原生分辨率编码",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500782&idx=1&sn=c45ad5e53f4bafee08d399f1d11d5189",
  "date": "2025-12-09 09:42:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：LLaVA-UHD</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3907407407407407\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"454\" data-imgfileid=\"100017118\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=253b5fb0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwtCjt5qZ8n2kZcX3bkKj0vTIiaggSQQyoou6h6T4VUbqABlErSRfPFt33vzhXKJyP4Yon9vMbjZhw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★LLaVA-UHD v3 是一个多模态大语言模型，基于我们提出的渐进视觉压缩（PVC）技术，实现了高效的原生分辨率编码。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型在15个不同基准测试中表现出与先进的多模态大语言模型（如Qwen2-VL）相当的性能，同时将首次令牌时间（TTFT）减少了1.9倍。此外，LLaVA-UHD v3 可以在学术环境中高效训练，约需300小时在32个A100 GPU上完成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/llavauhd\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/llavauhd</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：NetraEmbed</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.33796296296296297\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" data-height=\"394\" data-imgfileid=\"100017117\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=947d0e0e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwtCjt5qZ8n2kZcX3bkKj0viaxo1v1sCSicsrLfaT3pcAtkubJR9cam76cFp3DtxmCsZafnKLWibOgmg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★NetraEmbed是一个多语言多模态嵌入模型，专为视觉文档检索设计。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它通过Matryoshka表示学习将视觉文档和文本查询编码为单一的稠密向量，支持多种语言，并在多种嵌入维度（768, 1536, 2560）上实现高效的相似性搜索。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/netraembed\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/netraembed</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：GLM-4.6V</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.40370370370370373\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"470\" data-imgfileid=\"100017119\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c0e5de6e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwtCjt5qZ8n2kZcX3bkKj0vxOAMSjsJibelGZx0mibXNjXlPSjWA4YQMCCP6xBDaTOFLYFlQmQMBceA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★GLM-4.6V在视觉理解方面达到了同类参数规模中的最先进性能，并首次集成了原生功能调用能力，能够在真实业务场景中为多模态代理提供统一的技术基础</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。GLM-4.6V 支持高质量的混合媒体创作，能够处理多达 128K 个标记的多文档输入，直接解释格式丰富的页面。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/glm-4-6v\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/glm-4-6v</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Light-X</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.32314814814814813\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"376\" data-imgfileid=\"100017115\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ba46c500&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwtCjt5qZ8n2kZcX3bkKj0vB8CZQ5cFVtGIfyiavLXHPictbmHRYVWbVicMkAKa5FiaUllHDYcCLaIPUA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Light-X 是一个视频生成框架，能够从单目视频中进行可控渲染，实现视点和照明的双重控制。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">动态点云</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">捕捉几何和运动，并通过一致投影到相同几何体上提供照明线索，从而实现几何和照明信号的有效分离。Light-X 引入了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;Light-Syn</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，这是一种基于退化的管道，通过逆映射从野外单目视频中合成训练对，确保了静态、动态和 AI 生成场景的稳健训练。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/light-x\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/light-x</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：PATN-Predictive-Adversarial-Transformation-Network (PATN)</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5361111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"624\" data-imgfileid=\"100017120\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a61d7961&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwtCjt5qZ8n2kZcX3bkKj0vG92Fy7RWJsicXgSazUatHHMCapjgjC1wVapr7ABwIPkqibc56beicj3ag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">★</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">PATN是一个实时的隐私保护框架，能够从历史信号中主动生成未来的对抗扰动。</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">PATN的设计旨在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">保护移动传感器数据的隐私</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，特别是在序列模型中，通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">对抗性变换网络</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">来实现这一目标。</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该框架确保在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">不干扰正常任务功能</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的情况下，持续提供保护。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/patn-predictive-adversarial-transformation-network\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/patn-predictive-adversarial-transformation-network</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：VieNeu-TTS</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.43703703703703706\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" data-height=\"510\" data-imgfileid=\"100017121\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3206dc52&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwtCjt5qZ8n2kZcX3bkKj0vGD6jyI62bZDyI3OneLOtJ2gES7iby4JF6K1v5PdTM9UGw0Eb7swvkCw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★VieNeu-TTS是一个先进的越南语文本到语音（TTS）模型，支持即时语音克隆。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型在约1000小时的高质量越南语语音上进行了训练，是对VieNeu-TTS-140h的显著升级。它提供了更</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">准确</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">稳定</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的越南语发音，支持越南语和英语之间的无缝切换，并实现了更高保真度和一致性的语音克隆。该模型能够在CPU或GPU上生成24kHz的波形，支持完全离线的生产级语音合成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/vieneu-tts\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/vieneu-tts</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇总了多模态大语言模型 LLaVA-UHD、多语言嵌入模型 NetraEmbed、视觉理解模型 GLM-4.6V，以及视频生成框架 Light-X，隐私保护框架 PATN 和越南语文本到语音模型 VieNeu-TTS 等最新人工智能项目。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文汇总了多模态大语言模型 LLaVA-UHD、多语言嵌入模型 NetraEmbed、视觉理解模型 GLM-4.6V，以及视频生成框架 Light-X，隐私保护框架 PATN 和越南语文本到语音模型 VieNeu-TTS 等最新人工智能项目。",
